                <h1>Indebted NHS trusts "in shocking state"</h1>
                <ul id="article-metadata" class="clearfix">
                    <li class="published-date">
                        Thursday 15 December 2011
                    </li>
                    
                    <li class="rss-link not-for-print">
                        <a href="http://www.hi-mag.com/health-insurance/product-area/pmi/?service=rss" class="rss-feed" title="PMI RSS"><!-- . rss-feed --></a>
                    </li>
                    
                    <li class="sector-link not-for-print">
